name: Enyo
content:
Enyo was an orange-skinned Twi'lek female. In 21 ABY, she served as an instructor for the Jedi Order at Jedi Master Luke Skywalker's Academy on the planet Ossus. In that year, Enyo was briefly spotted by Skywalker as she was leading a group of younglings through a series of exercises with training blades. The session was conducted close to a cluster of temple buildings situated apart from Skywalker's hut. Subsequently, Enyo passed her duties to Jedi Padawan Ben Solo, the nephew of Skywalker, who started leading the training session just in time to catch the attention of Skywalker and the explorer Lor San Tekka.
Enyo appeared in Adam Christopher's 2022 novel Shadow of the Sith.
